{"id": 464, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于旅行箱，你有啥尴尬/优雅的吐槽？", "description": "一只超过20寸的箱子拖在身后，还怎么做来去如风的美男/女子。", "record_count": 1862, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607022009583cyAaPjIG9zqoYF7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-17T10:01:43Z", "options": [{"id": 8275, "content": "一想到要提着它挤火车——卒", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141699}, {"id": 8473, "content": "每次拉着箱子上下楼就觉得自己就是个男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146873}, {"id": 8985, "content": "皮箱死沉，净重9斤?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168732}, {"id": 8231, "content": "希望能有方便爬楼梯的机械设计...", "image": null, "praise_count": 316, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145961}, {"id": 8232, "content": "在火车上被啤酒瓜子的推车划开一道口子，依然顽强用到现在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 8235, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161920}, {"id": 8236, "content": "估计几楼几号理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161920}, {"id": 8237, "content": "轮子和拉手为啥坏得最快!", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155398}, {"id": 8239, "content": "人飞到了美国，而箱子却飞去了埃及", "image": null, "praise_count": 131, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 8240, "content": "说好的防水，还是偷偷从拉链缝里漏进去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 8241, "content": "无印良品那款大箱子好用吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138712}, {"id": 8243, "content": "为了全家出游，买了个30寸的，然后发现重量不可以以家庭为单位计算", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161914}, {"id": 8244, "content": "大部分的箱子，还真特么丑啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161945}, {"id": 8249, "content": "痛苦的是碰到天桥，花了吃奶的劲搬上天桥，还要花吐奶的劲搬下天桥，最后还被箱子砸到脚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161765}, {"id": 8250, "content": "地铁只有楼梯。不奢望电梯，连电扶梯都没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89616}, {"id": 8255, "content": "就算装了一卡车的东西 还是会有漏拿的玩意", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162032}, {"id": 8261, "content": "喜欢牵着旅行箱的感觉。可是！如果它有个风火轮就好了。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161312}, {"id": 8265, "content": "不带箱子坐飞机累赘，带着箱子除了坐飞机其他事情都累赘。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688}, {"id": 11083, "content": "万向轮，太TM容易坏 !（涙）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150923}, {"id": 8268, "content": "旅行箱已经在家躺了很久并没有时间粗去玩ಥ_ಥ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 8269, "content": "不戴套，新箱子一次就变“花瓜”。——想要箱子一直美美的，还不够伺候它的，像养了个佛爷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162099}, {"id": 8270, "content": "坐地铁时，皮箱会跑。必须手抓着或者把它倒在地上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162103}, {"id": 8271, "content": "遇到不平的路，发出哐哐哐宛如挖掘机的噪声。", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138266}, {"id": 8272, "content": "嗯学生党坐二等座的动车告诉我20寸的箱子放在哪！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161933}, {"id": 8789, "content": "rimowa托运箱真的比较容易被摔坏也不知道为什么???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152586}, {"id": 8284, "content": "我记得，我好像有一次，把旅行箱的密码锁，就轻松一拿，就下来了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 8797, "content": "我现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167618}, {"id": 8289, "content": "拉杆好像并不能好好地承受箱子的重量，常常担心它用到一半突然断掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149860}, {"id": 8545, "content": "好的太贵", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234907pGXgJVfK3QxYFsBL.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164907}, {"id": 8290, "content": "箱子永远都不够装。。。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156126}, {"id": 8291, "content": "女汉子就是这样养成的，但是内心其实渴望有一个男的帮一把…", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142518}, {"id": 8804, "content": "箱子被撞衫，错拿了人家的，差点被当成小偷。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167698}, {"id": 8294, "content": "在安检区没有什么能比瞬间被翻箱倒柜后飞出的骨灰级骚bra挡住前路的屌丝男更踌躇的了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 8295, "content": "前几天已设计出一个蜗轮蜗杆在内的机构让行李箱生成两条轨道??  然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162293}, {"id": 8296, "content": "前些天设计出包含蜗轮蜗杆在内德机构能使行李箱产生两条轨道，然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162293}, {"id": 8810, "content": "为了便宜200母上让回国时给她带个心仪已久了的箱子，然后我因为超重罚了1600୧(๑•̀⌄•́๑)૭", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167687}, {"id": 8300, "content": "因力量不够，箱子举不上行李架，只能四处张望企求男士帮助", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162361}, {"id": 8305, "content": "轮子再静音点 生怕别人不知道你是搬家来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147653}, {"id": 8306, "content": "每次拖上那东西，就感觉世界好大，不知道为什么！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160495}, {"id": 8307, "content": "爱马仕贵的我荷包哭了??", "image": "img/option/option/2016060423490582vEfPzd0jkwLGRD.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98842}, {"id": 8309, "content": "打车，，  下车，，，  箱子在车上   人却到了家?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155884}, {"id": 8313, "content": "总觉得旅行箱应该要有反重力系统", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162092}, {"id": 8314, "content": "每次从学校回家，或从家回学校，我的胳膊因为拉行李箱都要废上一两天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125792}, {"id": 8320, "content": "不能智能显示现在到底有多少斤吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155075}, {"id": 8321, "content": "我爱万向轮", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155075}, {"id": 8322, "content": "旅行箱和充电宝什么时候品牌联名出一个组合产品就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155075}, {"id": 8578, "content": "在忧伤26存的箱子该怎么扛到火车行李架上，我是女的눈_눈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139559}, {"id": 8323, "content": "坐高铁箱子放在座位前面腿完全伸不直 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161957}, {"id": 8327, "content": "yu u g g h", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149169}, {"id": 9357, "content": "看到我么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168737}]}